reviewText: This is not the orginal, this is a TV cut version.

I know this movie gets low reviews and it does have it's cheesy moments, but I am a huge Louis Mandylor fan so I love this movie.  I have been looking to replace a copy I lost about 9 years ago and was thrilled to see that Amazon had it.  I ordered it used and it arrived in great condition.  I couldn't be happier.
